---
title: Orzo & chickpea soup
description: Rustle up this healthy, low-fat, low-calorie soup with orzo, chickpeas, veg and a can of chopped tomatoes. Top with grated parmesan to serve
image: https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2023/10/Orzo-and-chickpea-soup-4740644.jpg?resize=768,713
course: Lunch
time required: 1 hour 20 minutes
servings: '8'
author: Ailsa Burt
nutrition:
  calories: 189 calories
  fat: 5 grams fat
  saturated fat: 1 grams saturated fat
  carbohydrates: 26 grams carbohydrates
  sugar: 6 grams sugar
  protein: 8 grams protein
  fiber: 5 grams fiber
  sodium: 0.4 milligram of sodium
cook time: 1 hour
